data.description: Welcome to your dream home retreat! This picturesque 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on a sprawling 10.55+/- acres, offering tranquility and ample space. Located close to Cave Run Lake, this property provides the perfect blend of nature and comfort. Spacious Bedrooms including a versatile bonus room that can easily be converted into a 6th bedroom, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or even a home office. Enjoy the luxury of multiple living areas, including a living room, dining room, and a cozy family room featuring a charming fireplace. Kitchen with ample cabinetry and breakfast area. Attached two-car garage, providing convenience. The property also boasts a detached garage, offering plenty of space for all your storage and workshop needs. Relax and unwind on the charming front porch or take in the scenic beauty from the rear deck, which overlooks the gorgeous land and a peaceful pond. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this idyllic property your forever home. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place to create lasting memories with loved ones, this home has it all! Call today.
